df.loc[df.country.isin(Region['EU']), 'region'] = 'Eu'

df.loc[df.country.isin(Region['CN']), 'region'] = 'China'

# divide experience to 4 groups
# age to 3 group
df['expc'] = pd.qcut(df.exp, 4)
df['agec'] = pd.qcut(df.age, 3)
